{"tid":1628083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"臨時政府無限期擱置，直至雙普選成功/中共派兵鎮壓為止。","createTime":"2019-10-05T23:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T01:21:51.000Z","uid":4396,"like":39,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0c633544293c43d5b9276cf183bf0d0cdc52c780","tid":1628083,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T23:39:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">臨時政府的提出時機未成熟，甚至會影響美國幫手的意欲。為顧全大局，我地無限期擱置該想法，直到雙普選成功/共產黨出兵鎮壓為止。<br />\n<br />\n我個人亦希望香港可以完全擺脫中共的操控，但真係未係時候呀各位手足！我跪求大家耐心等候，我地一定會勝利！<br />\n</span><br />\n同意請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不同意請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後請大家宣傳出去，重整旗鼓。我地要不斷反思先會贏。行錯一步就會死無葬身之地！"},{"pid":"bb56d44225a618da194155615108cf54312e6c35","tid":1628083,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T23:40:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cbd29e862429f28b22acc061833d06f2e66f07c","tid":1628083,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T23:40:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba18481664f0b0da7c55d174f876e3e61b10a2bc","tid":1628083,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T23:41:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62a12725d70ff75dcc772db531daf3711a7d6775","tid":1628083,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T23:42:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f57a09a9d46e683e2148b13ddff44a4162bb20c","tid":1628083,"uid":4396,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T23:42:50.000Z","msg":"求下大家，我唔想因爲咁而冇左美國幫忙"},{"pid":"5abc84aef8721a64a9748c931df3e2a93b11fa6d","tid":1628083,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T23:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a3f8d0d98af8e2f161d57f48ff2ac2d354f110","tid":1628083,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10